265
00:20:34,287 --> 00:20:36,915
Sé lo que hay que hacer.

266
00:20:37,666 --> 00:20:40,627
Nos licenciamos en marketing.

267
00:20:40,877 --> 00:20:42,003
Venimos a jugar.

268
00:20:42,921 --> 00:20:46,050
